	(gr_text "> The Grid. A digital frontier. I tried to picture clusters of information as they moved through the computer.\n> What did they look like? Ships? Motorcycles? Were the circuits like freeways? \n> I kept dreaming of a world I thought I'd never see. And then, one day, I got in."
		(at 486 144 0)
		(layer "F.SilkS")
		(uuid "8ac6a9db-5a70-44c3-a531-1be1c4efde2b")
		(effects
